      <description>&lt;p&gt;Package group &amp;ldquo;base&amp;rdquo; is replaced as &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.archlinux.org/news/base-group-replaced-by-mandatory-base-package-manual-intervention-required/&#34;&gt;meta package &amp;ldquo;base&amp;rdquo; on 2019-10-06&lt;/a&gt;. The biggest change introduced by this move is that the kernel pkg &lt;code&gt;linux&lt;/code&gt; is not part of &amp;ldquo;base&amp;rdquo; anymore.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
